# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Old tagra.eu PDF install guide (2015) — still referenced/fanned-out
# to by ChatGPT (confirmed via Collabim LLM analysis 2026-06-30) but
# the generic tagra.eu->tagra.app domain redirect below 404s it since
