https://www.tagra.eu/sites/default/files/prilohy/tagra-eu-instalace-programu.pdf  /manuals/how-to-install-tagra/  301!
https://tagra.eu/sites/default/files/prilohy/tagra-eu-instalace-programu.pdf      /manuals/how-to-install-tagra/  301!

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# tagra.eu is a domain alias only — tagra.app is the primary domain.
# Send all tagra.eu/* traffic straight to the equivalent tagra.app/*
# path (preserves the path; the path-specific rules further below
# then catch any legacy tagra.eu-Drupal-era paths on the second hop).
# Must come first so it wins before any path-only rule below.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
https://www.tagra.eu/*    https://tagra.app/:splat   301!
https://tagra.eu/*        https://tagra.app/:splat   301!

